835
01:04:01,138 --> 01:04:04,237
Napušten od Boga.

836
01:04:05,017 --> 01:04:08,529
Napušten od milosti.

837
01:04:08,647 --> 01:04:11,707
Neka mi Bog bude svedok,

838
01:04:12,378 --> 01:04:15,222
nikada odustati neću.

839
01:04:15,816 --> 01:04:18,578
Dok se ne nađemo licem u lice.

840
