1519
01:53:36,431 --> 01:53:41,530
Ako poginem, nemoj plakati Kozeta.

1520
01:53:41,994 --> 01:53:43,554
Hoćeš li plakati, Kozeta,

1521
01:53:47,722 --> 01:53:52,526
